{
  "stem": "964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't have any responsibility for these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were sitting there for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And one day, came a Russian-- because in the Polish Army was from lieutenant up, all the command was Russian in Polish uniforms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one day, a-- a captain came up with a Jeep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he forgot that we are-- we are three qualified mechanics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Without anything, without going in to get the permission to take us away, [LAUGHS] he took us out in the Jeep and drove us away into the transport company.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he got himself a bargain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had mechanics and good drivers that were reliable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But while we were going-- when the war came to an end, we had to go long trips.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what happened, the-- the-- the drivers and the soldiers, we slept over sometimes in a little town, in order, you know, to rest and go further.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These guys used to sip out-- take out the gasoline from the-- from the-- from the-- from the trucks and sell for vodka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the middle of the road, you're finding out this guy's stuck, because has no gasoline.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I asked him, well, what happened to the gasoline?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eh, they said, dah, dah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every time there used to be a convoy from 50 or 100 trucks, they put me in charge.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they knew I will get 'em back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, the guys would get stuck on the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One-- one-- one-- one case was we drove into a forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the Germans tried-- tried-- shooted-- throw in artillery there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everything was going upside-down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- we were in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
